Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic Surgery\NYu Otosaka, 15 yr old male\Nattending doctor: Dr. Koike
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it hurts.\NIt's only been two days since the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I move?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know. Ask the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12: Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Medoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like we planned,\Nwe were able to prevent a collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't call this an operation.\NThis is just dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just said dealing with it,\Nbut after the shot you didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what happened,\Nand how did I end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori! Is Tomori all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine. She's also here in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Kumagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Kumagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was all while you were busy saving \Nyourself with your own ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer\Nare you going to complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, you were the one that said\Nwe should bet on his ability to time-leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.56,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be. Kumagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you forget that?\N- Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys concluded\Nthat they didn't need your ability of time-leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even against the ability to collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they tried to hold it back\Nusing hostages as their shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the result of miscalculations\Non both ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are things like this\Ngoing to keep continuing from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the least, we had Maedomari\Nerase the memories of the culpits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, we don't know\Nwhen you are going to be targeted next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All in all, I'm glad\Nyou woke up safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of us were taking turns\Nkeeping watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I still have something I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't my big brother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let me punch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you need to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does all this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means that for your big brother,\NKumagami was his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ayumi! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as long as I stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they said you won't be able to see\Nfrom your right eye ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the accident was so big,\Nit should have killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be thankful just being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With rehabilitation, they said I could live\Na life that is almost the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is life at the facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is nice to me, so it is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Brother Shun\Nseems to be very disillusioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it makes me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother is...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have lost Ayumi\Nright in front of my eyes once before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Big Brother, Kumagami was \Nsomeone similar in standing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had died in this incident,\Nwhat would have happened to Ayumi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takajo... It really does feel like\Nit's been quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're in a lot more pain\Nthan I had imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a sight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For Otosaka in such a condition,\NI have brought this in for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lunch box with a keep-warm function.\NAnd the contents are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This scent. It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:06:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This is a memory we share,\Nthe beef tongue curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think I would be reunited\Nwith it here of all places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall feed it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of the days back in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! This truly is the taste\Nof our adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another bite, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There still is plenty left,\Nso eat up until you are bored of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how is Tomori doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her injuries are a lot less severe than you,\Nso she will be discharged soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've had \Nall sorts of hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry back to the student \Ncouncil together with Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The current student council where I'm alone\Nwith Yusarin is wonderful, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to visit—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Kurobane. Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I made this for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, can it be some cream stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing. You're correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin's handmade cream stew is cherished\Nin the Kurobane house as a source of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It works well for illness and injuries, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's why she brought me\Nhandmade cream stew that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Now, say aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty! I feel like\NI got a bit more energy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can never show Takajo a scene like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from a dead person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where do people go once they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My existence is like a balloon\Nthat Yusa is holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Yusa's ability is gone,\Nthe balloon will easily fly off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shouldn't you go visit\Nthe people you care about while you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I experienced something\Nthat put me near death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can be gone at any point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should go visit them while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's understandable\Nas I have already died once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think, I used to eat that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be our mom's best dish,\Nbut Yusa copied her and made it often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's just like my family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Yusa, I made my parents unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, you could say dying\Nwas the worst way to be a bad daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, go see your parents\Nbefore that ability is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that suggestion into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was I asleep again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question. What do your parents do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, they make soba noodles\Ndeep in the mountains in Nagano and serve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then, I suggest you go\Nvisit them sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't have any time left!\NYou should go immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure! I'll talk it out with my manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This indeed requires a \Nbit of getting used to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,South 503\NNao Tomori
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fairly Close to Last Supper,\N"Fair Supper" for short!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a show where celebrities introduce viewers\Nto their favorite gourmet food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.60,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She had a show like this\Nthat she made regular appearances in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which wouldn't be their last supper,\Nbut a supper fairly close to it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, surprisingly enough,\NI'll be introducing the Fair Supper for me, Yusarin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The restaurant is over there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, this is a soba restaurant\Nthat Yusarin's parents run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:16.36,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She used her work\Nto go see her parents, huh... Pretty good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the first time Yusarin has seen her folks\Nin a while, and she seems very happy about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the hand-made soba\Nand wild greens tempura set meal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, I'll have some of the soba!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dunking it into the dipping sauce\Nwith lots of condiments!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So tasty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next up, I'll have some mugwort tempura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is tasty too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With such a lack of vocabulary, I'm surprised\Nyou managed to become a food show host.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, to be honest, it tastes very ordinary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So ordinary that you can buy something similar\Nto eat at a convenience store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you suddenly saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, the love of my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the secret ingredient\Nto make this an exquisite meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is why it is this tasty. \NIt is very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just reminded me\Nof Misa just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, she was a delinquent with a bad mouth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she truly was a good girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good way of repaying your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.96,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16 years congrats <3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today is your 16th birthday, Big Brother Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu here would never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I used all of my skills\Nfor the first time in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good things will come <3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... So will you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow someone rehabilitating\Nto overexert themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's sweet, but it's tasty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the same flavor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe this is because of that secret ingredient\Nthat Misa was talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, next, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:57.48,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be able to only give an impression like this.\NI'm not one to criticize others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty, tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grats on getting all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm not fully well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a favor I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, I hear you've been\Nhere for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This hospital is all right.\NYou won't have to deal with the police here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More than that—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's just like how I was back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorists are all acting up overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Japan will become involved\Nin their activities soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami is no longer here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to us from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... It was rather sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to be discharged\Nfrom the hospital a bit earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd have a chat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything from your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said that Japan will soon be involved\Nin the activities of overseas terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother has all his life knocked out of him.\NHe seems like a different person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dangerous people may keep showing up\Nin the future, coming after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose anyone,\Nor make anyone miserable ever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there is something I could do with my powers,\NI'd like to do. But I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother's research facility\Nhas already ceated a vaccine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent creation of ability-wielders\Nthe next time the comet swings by, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everything will end if you loot\Nevery ability that exists in this world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the abilities\Nthat will be sprouting from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this has risks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to you after gaining thousands,\Neven tens of thousands, of special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might turn into a monster that can\Npotentially annihilate the entire human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even then, will you be able to\Nstay sane and hold yourself back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bluntly put, it would be a feat of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, it is something that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only method that I can think of\Nthat can save all of the ability-wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wasn't planning\Non having this talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, you came back from the future\Nin order to save Ayumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you came to rescue me and Kumagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought you were merely\Na fiend of cheating on tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but who you are now is \Nsomeone I can believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your opinion of me has \Nchanged so drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is way too reckless for it to be\None of my tactics. Please forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will leave you with that\Nfor today. Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's pretty reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're saying that this\Nis the only way, then I'll do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your motive is a bit weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, something like what happened\Nmay happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I want to be the one\Nthat saves you. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? A romance or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say that with such a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there was ever a time\Nfor you to think favorably of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've said this before in a different world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I threw myself into despair\Nand kept falling into an abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were there next to me,\Nwatching over me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a guess, but wasn't that\Nmy way of taking responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that still saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do you trip up from there\Nfor it to evolve into romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot comprehend at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like you need reasoning to fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're the one that \Nused it as a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, our compatibility \Nis absolutely the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it. "I'll be waiting."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For when I'll see you once again,\Nafter you save every single ability-wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we can become lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you overestimating\Nmy abilities just a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you really pull this off, I am sure to\Nunconditionally find Yu Otosaka dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has that increased your motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Rather suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then promise me that you'll come back.\NWe shall meet again. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll make sure to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you lie, cut off the tip\Nof a finger! Pinky promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a scary promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it was better than swallowing\Na thousand needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, start with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to loot every \Nsingle ability, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What I'm about to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly what it entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to apologize.\NThis will return me to a proper human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, I want you to listen\Nto what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will go plunder the ability of every wielder\Nall over the world, and save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm the strongest\Nof all ability-wielders, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to put Kumagami's life to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can say the same thing for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How he saved me so much by being at my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't even get\Nto say thanks to him in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that people important to me\Nwill no longer suffer misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling is the same for you\Nafter losing Kumagami, right Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I've already \Ntaken Tomori's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has already begun. I'm not turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.12,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,South 404\NPlastic Surgery\NYu Otosaka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's some determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, how are you going\Nto search for ability-wielders?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone close to the syndicate's leader\Nmust have an ability similar to Kumagami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, they can't possibly gather that many\Nability-wielders in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, Fly overseas. Leave Japan to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Kumagami, but we are still a big syndicate\Nthat unifies the ability-wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hold them down\Nuntil their abilities are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't at least do that much,\Nwe can't possibly look him in the eye again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, you were 16 right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to do this\Nbefore you lose your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the story from Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take our powers, too.\NIt might be of help to you, even by a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take my little sister's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means... In other \Nwords, you no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what it means.\NThis is a pretty sensible spot for me to fade out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what are we to do\Nif you're going to hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Otosaka. Come on, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll take the \Nabilities from you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did something happen..?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa... Actually, I have a letter\Nyour big sister entrusted us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:46.97,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Yusa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Yusa, it's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun hanging out with\Nthose guys from the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that I wanted to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, the one thing that \Nwas hard for me, Yusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was the fact that I wanted to be together\Nwith you all the time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but we ended up\Nmissing each other at all times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you more than anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, a dead person will act\Nlike a dead person, and bid farewell now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister was always together\Nwith all of you, wasn't she.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We had a lot of fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:19.17,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Yusa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case... I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, please make sure to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're friends\Nwho spent high school life together,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,despite all of us suffering \Nfrom a common illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.\NPlease take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is about all I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you speak looking at that,\Nyou can probably get by, even if minimally.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made this in one night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know what your\Nstandardized test scores are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, after all,\NI'm just a fiend of cheating on tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in return.\NI want you to hold onto this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, understood.\NI will hold onto this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel uneasy. Everything is so uncertain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I have to do this.\NBecause I am the only one that can do this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please take care during your trip.
